textBeforeTable: Overall Hotel Rating: Good location, out of the hustle & bustle of mainstream London, yet easy access to the West End & all we wanted to do. Pleasant welcome, very slow lift to 2nd floor, where we had been upgraded for … See More  free to a Superior Room, which in fact was very average & a bit tired including chipped furniture. Bathroom was also a bit tired but clean with nice toiletries, the bed was very comfortable &peaceful. To sum up nothing really wrong but did not inspire me to return, sorry.   Collapse  Stay Date: 01/08/15, a customer aged 65+ who stayed at 4* myhotel Bloomsbury in Tottenham Court Road wrote this review.
